Linux:
NOTE:  On Cygwin you must replace : with ; in classpaths

To run SafeFile_1 execute the following commands:

../../../../bin/rv-monitor mop/SafeFile.rvm

javac -cp ../../../../lib/rt.jar:. mop/SafeFileRuntimeMonitor.java SafeFile_1/SafeFile_1.java

java -cp ../../../../lib/rt.jar:. SafeFile_1.SafeFile_1

To run SafeFile_2 execute the following commands:

../../../../bin/rv-monitor mop/SafeFile.rvm

javac -cp ../../../../lib/rt.jar:. mop/SafeFileRuntimeMonitor.java SafeFile_2/SafeFile_2.java

java -cp ../../../../lib/rt.jar:. SafeFile_2.SafeFile_2
